@Comment:	Time is 4:27
@Comment:	I Love you and come over. maybE we can come over to see you. we missieou. Chi love (five hearts are drawn at the bottom)
@Comment:	Chi decides to write to his auntie Rose but doesn't write that down. Chi knows what he wants to write right away. Mot helps later with what to say. Mot helps with spelling and tries to get Chi to leave more space between words. Mot get impatient at the end when Chi starts drawing hearts on the letter
